</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left">'full-width'</td>
<td style="text-align:left">Sets the tab header to display evenly across the entire width instead of left justified</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td style="text-align:left">'no-border'</td>
<td style="text-align:left">Removes the bottom border of the tabs header</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table>
